| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0326 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 004f8d6f-da6b-58b3-8f7d-2a5a31490e95"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
